Package extended_mitre.cwe

Class CWEextRefObj

  • java.lang.Object
    • extended_mitre.cwe.CWEextRefObj
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    @Entity(name="ext_ref")
public class CWEextRefObj
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents a CWE external reference object (reference ID attribute, author attributes, )

    It can create a CWE external reference object from given parameters and return it

    Objects can be put into database

    It also can go through file with CWE weaknesses or CAPEC objects, find external reference objects, parse them into CWE external reference objects and return them

    Author:
    Tomas Bozek (XarfNao)

      • CWEextRefToArrayList

        public static java.util.List<CWEextRefObj> CWEextRefToArrayList​(java.lang.String file)
        This method's purpose is to go through file with CWE weaknesses or CAPEC objects, find external reference objects, parse them into CWE external reference objects and return them

        It uses DOM XML parser

        If it can't find any informations, it returns these attributes as null values

        Parameters:
        file - path to an XML file which will be parsed from
        Returns:
        list of parsed CWE external reference objects
